descript.abstract: This dataset includes the counties (and independent cities in Virginia) that make up the Commuter Shed region. This file shows detailed coastlines.
descript.purpose: Downloaded 2010 TIGER files for the Counties shapefiles for the states of DE,MD,PA,VA,WVA and DC from the Census website. Merged the Counties files together, then selected the counties that make up TPBComm. Used Major_Water to carve out the coastlines. After TPBComm was built, selected out the counties that make up TPBMod.
